beer.beer_description:
Morning Star Belgian Dark Ale is the darker, powerful partner to our Guardian Belgian Tripel. 

Expect strong dark fruit flavours, raisins and big bready malt characters that meld beautifully with the Belgian yeast characters of pear, black pepper, clove and banana.

This 7.1% Belgian Dark Ale is a lavish dark copper hue. It is spicy, brooding and decadent.
